---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
---

<BaseLayout title="Let Us Help" wide={true} description="How a Google Ads Solutions Architect can help your business grow.">
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="google-bar"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></div>
    <h1>How We Can Help</h1>
    <p class="subtitle">As your <strong>Google Ads Solutions Architect</strong>, we combine deep technical expertise with strategic business thinking to accelerate your growth.</p>
  </section>

  <!-- What a Solutions Architect Does -->
  <section class="section">
    <h2>What a Solutions Architect Does</h2>
    <p class="intro">A Solutions Architect at Google (gTech Ads) is a trusted technical advisor for large, strategic partners. We bridge the gap between complex advertising technology and real business outcomes.</p>

    <div class="card-grid">
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-icon blue">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M2 3h6a4 4 0 0 1 4 4v14a3 3 0 0 0-3-3H2z"/><path d="M22 3h-6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v14a3 3 0 0 1 3-3h7z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Technical Consulting</h3>
        <p>Design and implement advanced Google Ads solutions — from conversion tracking architecture to API integrations, automated bidding strategies, and data pipeline setup.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-icon red">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M12 20V10"/><path d="M18 20V4"/><path d="M6 20v-4"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Strategic Planning</h3>
        <p>Translate business objectives into advertising strategies. We help set KPIs, plan budgets across channels, and build measurement frameworks that prove real ROI.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-icon yellow">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="M12 6v6l4 2"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Optimization at Scale</h3>
        <p>Audit existing campaigns, identify wasted spend, and implement systematic improvements. We work across Search, Shopping, YouTube, Display, and Performance Max.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-icon green">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H5a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/><path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"/><path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Partner Enablement</h3>
        <p>Train your teams on Google Ads best practices, build internal capabilities, and create playbooks so your organization can scale independently.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-icon blue">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="16 18 22 12 16 6"/><polyline points="8 6 2 12 8 18"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Technical Implementation</h3>
        <p>Hands-on support with Google Tag Manager, server-side tagging, enhanced conversions, GA4 integration, BigQuery exports, and Google Ads scripts automation.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-icon red">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"/><polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Problem Solving</h3>
        <p>Diagnose performance drops, fix tracking issues, resolve policy violations, troubleshoot bidding problems, and unblock scaling challenges.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Key Responsibilities -->
  <section class="section alt-bg">
    <h2>Key Responsibilities</h2>
    <div class="resp-grid">
      <div class="resp-item">
        <span class="resp-num">01</span>
        <h3>Manage Ads Solutions</h3>
        <p>Manage the implementation of Ads solutions for large, strategic partners across Southeast Asia. Guide product strategy and technical integrations end-to-end.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="resp-item">
        <span class="resp-num">02</span>
        <h3>Analyze & Recommend</h3>
        <p>Analyze partner business needs, translate them into technical requirements, and recommend the right mix of Google Ads products and features.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="resp-item">
        <span class="resp-num">03</span>
        <h3>Drive Adoption</h3>
        <p>Drive adoption of new Google Ads features and best practices. Stay ahead of product launches, betas, and industry changes to give partners early advantages.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="resp-item">
        <span class="resp-num">04</span>
        <h3>Cross-functional Collaboration</h3>
        <p>Work with Sales, Product, and Engineering teams to surface partner needs, influence product roadmaps, and escalate critical technical issues.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="resp-item">
        <span class="resp-num">05</span>
        <h3>Measure Impact</h3>
        <p>Build measurement frameworks, run experiments, and quantify the business impact of every recommendation to ensure partners see real results.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="resp-item">
        <span class="resp-num">06</span>
        <h3>Scale Knowledge</h3>
        <p>Create scalable solutions — documentation, playbooks, automation scripts — that benefit not just one partner but the entire ecosystem.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- The Google Way: How We Think -->
  <section class="section">
    <h2>The Google Way: How We Think</h2>
    <p class="intro">At Google, Solutions Architects are evaluated on four core attributes that go beyond technical skills. These shape how we approach every partner engagement.</p>

    <div class="attr-grid">
      <div class="attr-card">
        <div class="attr-icon">
          <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#4285f4" stroke-width="2"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="M9.09 9a3 3 0 0 1 5.83 1c0 2-3 3-3 3"/><line x1="12" y1="17" x2="12.01" y2="17"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>General Cognitive Ability</h3>
        <p class="attr-quote">"We ask open-ended questions to learn how you approach and solve problems. There's no one right answer — your ability to explain your thought process and how you use data to inform decisions is what's most important."</p>
        <div class="attr-how">
          <h4>How this helps you:</h4>
          <ul>
            <li>We don't jump to cookie-cutter solutions — we diagnose your specific situation first</li>
            <li>Every recommendation is backed by data, not assumptions</li>
            <li>We think through second-order effects before making changes</li>
            <li>We ask the right questions to understand what's really driving (or hurting) your performance</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="attr-card">
        <div class="attr-icon">
          <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#ea4335" stroke-width="2"><path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H5a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/><path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"/><path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Leadership</h3>
        <p class="attr-quote">"Be prepared to discuss how you have used your communication and decision-making skills to mobilize others — by stepping up to a leadership role or by helping a team succeed even when you weren't officially the leader."</p>
        <div class="attr-how">
          <h4>How this helps you:</h4>
          <ul>
            <li>We align your marketing, product, and engineering teams around shared goals</li>
            <li>We make clear recommendations and own the outcomes — not just hand off a report</li>
            <li>We drive cross-functional projects (tracking implementation, feed setup, migration) to completion</li>
            <li>We push back constructively when we see a strategy that won't work</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="attr-card">
        <div class="attr-icon">
          <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#fbbc05" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="16 18 22 12 16 6"/><polyline points="8 6 2 12 8 18"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Role-Related Knowledge</h3>
        <p class="attr-quote">"We're interested in how your individual strengths combine with your experience to drive impact. We don't just look for how you can contribute today, but how you can grow into different roles — including ones that haven't been invented yet."</p>
        <div class="attr-how">
          <h4>How this helps you:</h4>
          <ul>
            <li>Deep expertise across the full Google Ads ecosystem — Search, Shopping, Video, PMax, Display</li>
            <li>Technical depth in tracking, APIs, scripts, data feeds, and measurement</li>
            <li>Understanding of both B2B and B2C strategies across industries</li>
            <li>We stay current on new features, betas, and industry shifts so you don't have to</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="attr-card">
        <div class="attr-icon">
          <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#34a853" stroke-width="2"><path d="M20.84 4.61a5.5 5.5 0 0 0-7.78 0L12 5.67l-1.06-1.06a5.5 5.5 0 0 0-7.78 7.78l1.06 1.06L12 21.23l7.78-7.78 1.06-1.06a5.5 5.5 0 0 0 0-7.78z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Googleyness</h3>
        <p class="attr-quote">"Share how you work individually and on a team, how you help others, how you navigate ambiguity, and how you push yourself to grow outside of your comfort zone."</p>
        <div class="attr-how">
          <h4>How this helps you:</h4>
          <ul>
            <li>We're genuinely invested in your success — not just hitting metrics</li>
            <li>We're transparent about trade-offs, risks, and what we don't know</li>
            <li>We bring energy and optimism even to messy, ambiguous challenges</li>
            <li>We share knowledge freely — our goal is to make you self-sufficient, not dependent</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- How We Work With Partners -->
  <section class="section alt-bg">
    <h2>How We Work With Partners</h2>
    <div class="process-grid">
      <div class="process-step">
        <div class="step-circle blue">1</div>
        <h3>Discovery</h3>
        <p>We start by understanding your business — goals, constraints, audience, competitive landscape, and current advertising maturity.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="process-step">
        <div class="step-circle red">2</div>
        <h3>Audit & Diagnose</h3>
        <p>Deep audit of your current setup — account structure, tracking, bidding, creative, and landing pages. We identify quick wins and structural issues.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="process-step">
        <div class="step-circle yellow">3</div>
        <h3>Strategy & Roadmap</h3>
        <p>We build a prioritized action plan with clear milestones, expected impact, and resource requirements. No 50-page decks — actionable steps.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="process-step">
        <div class="step-circle green">4</div>
        <h3>Implement & Optimize</h3>
        <p>Hands-on implementation alongside your team. We build, test, measure, iterate — and train your team to sustain the improvements.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="cta-section">
    <h2>Ready to grow?</h2>
    <p>Explore our resources or ask the chatbot anything about Google Ads.</p>
    <div class="cta-links">
      <a href={base} class="cta-btn primary">Talk to the chatbot</a>
      <a href={`${base}projects/google-ads/`} class="cta-btn">Read the complete guide</a>
      <a href={`${base}success-story`} class="cta-btn">View success stories</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .hero {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 2.5rem 0 2rem;
  }

  .google-bar {
    display: flex; height: 4px; border-radius: 2px; overflow: hidden;
    max-width: 80px; margin: 0 auto 1.5rem;
  }
  .google-bar span { flex: 1; }
  .google-bar span:nth-child(1) { background: var(--color-google-blue); }
  .google-bar span:nth-child(2) { background: var(--color-google-red); }
  .google-bar span:nth-child(3) { background: var(--color-google-yellow); }
  .google-bar span:nth-child(4) { background: var(--color-google-green); }

  .hero h1 {
    font-size: 2.25rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--color-text);
    margin: 0 0 0.75rem; letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }

  .subtitle {
    font-size: 1.05rem; color: var(--color-text-muted); margin: 0 auto;
    max-width: 600px; line-height: 1.65;
  }

  .section { padding: 2.5rem 0; }
  .section.alt-bg {
    background: #f8f9fa; margin: 0 -1.5rem; padding: 2.5rem 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 16px;
  }

  .section h2 {
    font-size: 1.6rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--color-text);
    margin: 0 0 0.75rem;
  }

  .intro {
    font-size: 0.95rem; color: var(--color-text-muted); margin: 0 0 1.5rem;
    max-width: 640px; line-height: 1.65;
  }

  /* Card grid */
  .card-grid {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .card {
    background: white; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 1.25rem 1.35rem; transition: box-shadow 0.15s, transform 0.15s;
  }
  .card:hover { box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.06); transform: translateY(-1px); }

  .card-icon {
    width: 40px; height: 40px; border-radius: 10px;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    margin-bottom: 0.85rem;
  }
  .card-icon.blue { background: #e8f0fe; }
  .card-icon.red { background: #fce8e6; }
  .card-icon.yellow { background: #fef7e0; }
  .card-icon.green { background: #e6f4ea; }
  .card-icon.blue svg { stroke: #1a73e8; }
  .card-icon.red svg { stroke: #ea4335; }
  .card-icon.yellow svg { stroke: #f9ab00; }
  .card-icon.green svg { stroke: #34a853; }

  .card h3 {
    font-size: 0.95rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--color-text);
    margin: 0 0 0.4rem;
  }
  .card p {
    font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--color-text-muted); margin: 0; line-height: 1.6;
  }

  /* Responsibilities */
  .resp-grid {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.25rem;
  }
  .resp-item { display: flex; gap: 0.85rem; align-items: flex-start; }
  .resp-num {
    font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 700; color: #dadce0;
    flex-shrink: 0; min-width: 36px;
  }
  .resp-item h3 {
    font-size: 0.92rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--color-text); margin: 0 0 0.3rem;
  }
  .resp-item p {
    font-size: 0.84rem; color: var(--color-text-muted); margin: 0; line-height: 1.6;
  }

  /* Google attributes */
  .attr-grid {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.25rem;
  }

  .attr-card {
    background: white; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; border-radius: 14px;
    padding: 1.5rem; transition: box-shadow 0.15s;
  }
  .attr-card:hover { box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.06); }

  .attr-icon { margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
  .attr-card h3 {
    font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--color-text); margin: 0 0 0.5rem;
  }
  .attr-quote {
    font-size: 0.84rem; color: var(--color-text-muted); font-style: italic;
    line-height: 1.65; margin: 0 0 0.85rem; padding-left: 0.75rem;
    border-left: 3px solid #e5e7eb;
  }
  .attr-how h4 {
    font-size: 0.8rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--color-google-blue);
    margin: 0 0 0.3rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.03em;
  }
  .attr-how ul {
    margin: 0; padding-left: 1.1rem; font-size: 0.84rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted); line-height: 1.65;
  }
  .attr-how li { margin-bottom: 0.25rem; }

  /* Process */
  .process-grid {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(220px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.25rem;
  }
  .process-step { text-align: center; }
  .step-circle {
    width: 48px; height: 48px; border-radius: 50%; margin: 0 auto 0.75rem;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 700; color: white;
  }
  .step-circle.blue { background: #4285f4; }
  .step-circle.red { background: #ea4335; }
  .step-circle.yellow { background: #fbbc05; color: #202124; }
  .step-circle.green { background: #34a853; }
  .process-step h3 {
    font-size: 0.92rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--color-text); margin: 0 0 0.3rem;
  }
  .process-step p {
    font-size: 0.84rem; color: var(--color-text-muted); margin: 0; line-height: 1.6;
  }

  /* CTA */
  .cta-section {
    text-align: center; padding: 2.5rem 0 1rem;
  }
  .cta-section h2 {
    font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--color-text); margin: 0 0 0.5rem;
  }
  .cta-section p {
    font-size: 0.92rem; color: var(--color-text-muted); margin: 0 0 1.25rem;
  }
  .cta-links { display: flex; gap: 0.75rem; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .cta-btn {
    padding: 0.55rem 1.25rem; border-radius: 100px; font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 500; text-decoration: none; transition: all 0.15s;
    border: 1px solid #dadce0; color: var(--color-text);
  }
  .cta-btn:hover { background: #f3f4f6; }
  .cta-btn.primary {
    background: #1a73e8; border-color: #1a73e8; color: white;
  }
  .cta-btn.primary:hover { background: #1557b0; }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .hero h1 { font-size: 1.75rem; }
    .card-grid, .attr-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }
</style>
